React Fragments:


Sometimes the wrapper div is irrelevant and it's used because components require to return only one element.

***********Before***********
<div>
	<td>Hello</td>
    <td>World</td>
</div>
***********After************
<React.Fragment>
        <td>Hello</td>
        <td>World</td>
</React.Fragment>

jsx or js :
It does not matter, jsx are converted to js. JSX is used for saying that a file contains only jsx code.

